<p class=Char style='text-indent:26.25pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.5'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold'>1. Our merchant
have right fight the chargeback, the appeal files need add to merchant admin
panel before deadline.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=Char style='margin-left:41.6pt;mso-para-margin-left:2.2gd;text-indent:
-15.2pt;mso-char-indent-count:-1.45'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;
mso-bidi-font-weight:bold'>2. After submit appeal materials, the acquiring bank
will audit the materials upfront. Regarding the merchant not provide the
materials and proofs as request, the bank can not appeal with international
card organization, and the chargeback effect. So please check the <span
class=GramE>materials<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp; </span>very</span>
carefully when you submit, make sure everything is ready as request. During
appeal, if card organization judgment we win<span class=GramE>,<span
style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp; </span>the</span> issuing card bank will
undertake all the relate cost; if the international card organization judge we
lost the case, the merchant undertake the transaction cost, will not generate
extra cost. The merchant can <span class=SpellE>initate</span> arbitration
request, if the merchant lost the arbitration again, not only need undertake
transaction loss, but also the fees <span class=GramE>below :</span><o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=Char style='text-indent:41.7pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.97'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold'>International
organization arbitration/compliance handing <span class=GramE>fee :</span> 250
USD<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=Char style='text-indent:41.7pt;mso-char-indent-count:3.97'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold'>International
organization arbitration/compliance arbitration <span class=GramE>fee :250</span>
USD, totally 500 USD.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=Char style='text-indent:26.25pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.5'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold'>3. If not provide
the materials on time, default accept chargeback.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=Char style='margin-left:47.0pt;mso-para-margin-left:2.2gd;text-indent:
-20.6pt;mso-char-indent-count:-1.96'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.5pt;
mso-bidi-font-weight:bold'>4. Suggest communicate with clients, and had better
persuade cardholder give up chargeback. <span class=GramE>Remind :</span>
Sometimes because the cardholder can not remember descriptor caused the
chargeback,<span style='mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp; </span>please indicate the
descriptor when contact the cardholder.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=Char style='text-indent:26.25pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.5'><span
